constituent: riddle, say, words, keitai, mouth, astray, rice, road
koohiiStory1: Words meant to lead you astray are those of a riddle.
koohiiStory2: I led Socrates astray with my riddle. He quit philosophizing and thought only about the riddle.
myStory: chữ mê. câu đố, điều bí ẩn. ngôn ngữ gây lạc đường là câu đố. ngôn + mê
